Package: networkViz
Title: R interface to nfpm visualization
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c( person("Jayaram", "Kancherla", 
                      email="jayaram.kancherla@gmail.com",
                      role = c("aut", "cre")
                    )
            )
Description: This package provides an API for interactive network visualization of gene-drug and gene-gene interactions.
             The focus of a visualization is the flow of evidence between various does and uses an interactive sankey diagram
             to visualize the network.
Imports:
    htmltools,
    rjson,
    methods
